I was wondering if there are any recommended guidelines for architecting
DNS for a site (~1500 nodes).  For example,  # of authoritative servers,
# of resolvers per node, locality (e.g. no more than 1 bridge or repeater
away, etc.)?  Any RFC's or other documents I can reference?

-&gt;dave

